<p>We use <strong>cookies</strong> to store some data.  We only use this so user does not have to enter everything again. By using this site, you agree to the use of cookies.</p>
<p style="color:red">The cookies expire within a day.</p>

<p>It is probably a good idea to have additional secret characters that you append or prepend to the generated password. An example is to add special characters at the end of the password and use that. This way, even if someone snooped while you were generating the password, they would have to guess the additional characters that you only know (unless they have a keylogger)</p>

